Sec 3.3.1

# p. 51
joseph <- BabynamesDist %>%
  filter(name == "Joseph" & sex == "M")
name_plot <- ggplot(data = joseph, aes(x = year))
name_plot <- name_plot +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity",
           aes(y = count_thousands * alive_prob),
           fill = "#b2d7e9", color = "white")
name_plot

# p. 51
name_plot <- name_plot +
  geom_line(aes(y = count_thousands), size = 2)
name_plot <- name_plot +
  ylab("Number of People (thousands)") +
  xlab(NULL)
name_plot

# p. 52
wtd.quantile <- Hmisc::wtd.quantile
median_yob <- joseph %>%
  with(wtd.quantile(year, est_alive_today, probs = 0.5))
median_yob

# p. 52
name_plot <- name_plot +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", color = "white", fill = "#008fd5",
           aes(y = ifelse(year == median_yob, est_alive_today / 1000, 0)))
name_plot

# p. 52
name_plot +
  ggtitle("Age Distribution of American Boys Name Joseph") +
  geom_text(x = 1935, y = 40, label = "Number of Josephs\nborn each year") +
  geom_text(x = 1915, y = 13,
            label = "Number of Joseph\nborn each year\n
              estimated to be alive\non 1/1/2014",

  geom_text(x = 2003, y = 40,
